    <data key="d0">Vizio Smart TV Telemetry Pipeline</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BlCXEMp_lqY</data>
    <data key="d2">DATA_PEEK: Millions of devices generating billions of events per month. WORKLOAD_PEEK: Serverless telemetry ingestion using an 8-shard Kinesis pipeline, S3 data lake archiving, and Redshift warehousing.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, interactive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
